p.k: New European Championship Wrestling (NEW) slaví své páté výročí s akcí "High Explosive IV" nabitou wrestlingem
p.d: New European Championship Wrestling (NEW) celebrates its 5th year anniversary with the action-packed wrestling event "High Explosive IV". Five years ago it all began, when former WCW World Champion Alex Wright presented the first event "High Explosive I". See great athletes, tough matches, super entertainment and experience this show in the most unique location, the N.E.W. HotSpot, Germany's only individually equipped wrestling hall. Are you ready for... HIGH EXPLOSIVE IV!
